    "# Advanced AI Model Training Workflow\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook implements the complete AI model training workflow as described in the project README. It covers:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Dataset Handling** - Loading and preprocessing multiple datasets\n",
    "2. **Model Architecture** - Creating a transformer-based model architecture\n",
    "3. **Training Process** - Fine-tuning the model on the datasets\n",
    "4. **Evaluation** - Assessing model performance with appropriate metrics\n",
    "5. **Deployment Preparation** - Ensuring compatibility with Flask and CoreML\n",
    "\n",
    "We'll use the repository's utilities for all aspects of the workflow, creating a high-performance AI model capable of diverse tasks."
   ]
  },
